title: Open Up Cautions
itunes:title: Open Up Cautions
description:
Today on the show we had Kevin O'Leary better known as Mr. Wonderful from Shark Tank stopped by to speak on StartEngine, Shark Tank, Smart Business, and today's market. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to a dead man for getting a hard attack for burying his girlfriend that he killed. Also, Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee" with one listener that is tired of her boyfriend opening up to her physically and emotionally. 

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
